{
  "stem": "15193.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when my husband came out, he got-- he was offered a job to clear the debris from the bombing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my husband said, what do you think about it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, I wouldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, that's good money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, money here, money there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Your hands are your future.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If, God forbid, something happens to your hand, that is the end of that story.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he found a job as a watchmaker in a jewelry store, and he worked as a watchmaker.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the afternoons, we had our own clientele.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We then made sure because watchmakers were very, very hard to come by.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had the most important customers you ever can imagine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was one customer, he was from the Scotland Yard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When my husband worked already, and he brought us some watches, and we repaired them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one day, he wanted us to go to his home in the country by train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he said, and I want you to take a little trunk along and keep it locked.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Give it to my mother and never open it before you get home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my husband went there and gave them the trunk and repaired the clock and came back, no, no problems.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when we opened, it was full of chickens, which we hadn't seen in years, eggs-- we hadn't seen in years-- butter, and everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we shared it with our friends because otherwise, it gets bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I tell you, we were received-- once they found out who we were, they were nice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, to be very honest with you, the neighbors of the apartment we lived in were very strange.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came from the Isle of Wight, and they did not believe in foreigners.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
